    • setAddVectorAsNullable

      public void setAddVectorAsNullable(boolean nullable)
      Set flag to control the FieldType.nullable property when a writer creates a new vector. If true then vectors created will be nullable, this is the default behavior. If false then vectors created will be non-nullable.
      Parameters:
      nullable - Whether or not to create nullable vectors (default behavior is true)
